JOHANNESBURG - Bloomberg journalist Sam Mkokeli was forcibly removed from Nasrec, the venue of the ANC national conference, on Tuesday. Mkokeli, a member of the SA National Editors' Forum, said his accreditation was removed. Other journalists, including PowerFM's Iman Rapetti and Fin24's Jan de Lange, tried to intervene, to no avail. The incident was roundly condemned. eNCA